{"results":[{"aya":"001","id":5376,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"有人曾请求一种将发生的刑罚。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"002","id":5377,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"那是为不信的人们而预定的，没有任何人能加以抵抗。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"003","id":5378,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"那是真主--天梯的主宰--发出的，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"004","id":5379,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"众天神和精神在一日之内升到他那里。那一日的长度是五万年。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"005","id":5380,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"你安然地忍受吧。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"006","id":5381,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"他们以为那刑罚是很远的，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"007","id":5382,"locale":"zh","sura":"070","text":"我却以为那是很近的。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":7,"nextPage":"/zh/s070-2.json"}}